{"tid":448213,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧厄卡斯莫度膺fifa18最廢球員","createTime":"2017-10-26T04:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T05:15:55.000Z","uid":54747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a0fdf1b437513d015ca4fd3193a3bcf504c58d","tid":448213,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"大家都會留意電玩足球遊戲《FIFA 18》中，球星的能力值是多少，究竟最低值的是哪一位？<br />\n<br />\n原來是效力德乙球隊奧厄的卡斯莫度（Tommy Kassmodel）！今季從未上陣過的他，總能力值在爆標的99當中，只得46；速度23、射門42、傳送48、運球45、防守36、體能38。數字很差對不對？<br />\n<br />\n因為他根本不是所說的中場，而是奧厄的球衣管理員。不過，球隊真的把他註冊為球員，因為每支德國球隊的一隊，都需要有4名從青年軍提升的球員，而29歲的卡斯莫度正正合乎這要求，因此被拿來填數。<br />\n<br />\n至於《FIFA 18》中，最強的是代言人兼新鮮出爐的國際足協最佳球員基斯坦奴朗拿度，總能力值有95！未知大家有沒有興趣，在遊戲中使用卡斯莫度來跟C朗單挑？<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 互聯網"},{"pid":"7a99e41fdcf7ca1b51356810f7ddb7710a59c31b","tid":448213,"uid":74081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:24:33.000Z","msg":"小馬呢？"},{"pid":"c6bd929805e4faba986fb4628a3b16f13dddaffa","tid":448213,"uid":33497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f092c560cbb02105fcd114deb2301202e20e4407","tid":448213,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:56:58.000Z","msg":"覺得佢好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0af1ac77e443986cda5f9d5a9b358b631e7063","tid":448213,"uid":92465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"c朗95<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493aec46d3359aa9198eb19df6077114f4687108","tid":448213,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"速度23<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> fifa成日將d屎波既球員定左型一定係唔識跑步"},{"pid":"6fcfcb6db044e4b5b631e7b3109ea15675aae4ed","tid":448213,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit